					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-darkgray mb-6">
						ADVANCED AIR PURIFICATION SOLUTIONS FOR YOUR HOME
					</h3>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						Indoor air can contain a variety of pollutants that affect your health and comfort, from allergens and dust
						to harmful microorganisms and chemical pollutants. At Alltek Services, we offer advanced air purification
						systems designed to effectively remove these contaminants and create a healthier living environment.
					</p>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						Our air purification solutions utilize cutting-edge technology to capture and eliminate airborne particles,
						allergens, bacteria, viruses, mold spores, and volatile organic compounds (VOCs). Whether you're concerned
						about allergies, asthma, or simply want to improve the overall air quality in your home, we have a solution
						that fits your needs.
					</p>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-8">
						Our expert technicians will help you select the right air purification system for your home based on your
						specific air quality concerns, the size of your space, and your budget. We offer a range of options, from
						whole-home systems that integrate with your HVAC system to standalone units for targeted purification in
						specific areas.
					</p>
